{"text_id":73149,"tokens":["Title",":"," Shaping"," the"," Glob","ular"," Cluster"," Mass"," Function"," by"," Stellar","-","Dyna","mical"," Evaporation","\n\n","Abstract",":","\n","In"," this"," study",","," we"," investigate"," the"," influence"," of"," stellar","-","dyna","mical"," evaporation"," on"," the"," mass"," function"," of"," globular"," clusters","."," Our"," motivation"," stems"," from"," the"," observed"," discrepancies"," between"," the"," initial"," and"," present","-","day"," mass"," functions"," of"," globular"," clusters",","," which"," suggest"," significant"," mass"," loss"," over"," time","."," We"," aim"," to"," elucidate"," the"," role"," of"," stellar","-","dyna","mical"," processes"," in"," shaping"," these"," mass"," functions","."," Utilizing"," a"," combination"," of"," N","-","body"," simulations"," and"," semi","-","analytical"," models",","," we"," analyze"," the"," evolution"," of"," globular"," clusters"," under"," the"," influence"," of"," two","-","body"," relaxation"," and"," tidal"," interactions","."," We"," focus"," on"," quanti","fying"," the"," rate"," of"," mass"," loss"," and"," its"," dependence"," on"," cluster"," parameters"," such"," as"," initial"," mass",","," density",","," and"," orbital"," characteristics","."," Our"," findings"," indicate"," that"," stellar","-","dyna","mical"," evaporation"," significantly"," alters"," the"," mass"," distribution",","," preferentially"," deple","ting"," low","-","mass"," clusters"," and"," leading"," to"," a"," skewed"," present","-","day"," mass"," function","."," This"," work"," addresses"," the"," critical"," problem"," of"," recon","ciling"," theoretical"," models"," with"," observational"," data",","," providing"," insights"," into"," the"," long","-","term"," dynamical"," evolution"," of"," globular"," clusters","."," Our"," results"," have"," implications"," for"," understanding"," the"," formation"," and"," survival"," of"," these"," ancient"," stellar"," systems",",","